LounGenie Portal
================

VERSION:            1.0.0 - PRODUCTION READY
RELEASE DATE:       December 18, 2025
STATUS:             ✅ APPROVED FOR LIVE DEPLOYMENT
ENVIRONMENT:        Shared WordPress Hosting

TARGET SPECS:
- PHP 7.4+
- WordPress 5.8+
- MySQL 5.7+ or MariaDB 10.3+
- Memory: 128MB per request
- Disk: 5GB minimum

WHAT'S INCLUDED:
✅ Multi-role portal (Support, Partner)
✅ Ticket management (create, reply, update status)
✅ REST API (8 endpoints)
✅ Audit logging (immutable, SOC2-ready)
✅ File attachments (with size/MIME validation)
✅ Email integration (inbound/outbound)
✅ Microsoft SSO (Azure AD support staff)
✅ CRM sync (HubSpot)
✅ Capability-based access control
✅ Versioned database migrations
✅ Standardized error codes
✅ CSP headers (security)
✅ Rate limiting framework

WHAT'S NOT INCLUDED (v2.0+):
❌ Real-time gateway telemetry
❌ WebSockets
❌ Background workers
❌ Mobile app
❌ White-label
❌ Advanced analytics

SHARED HOSTING CONSTRAINTS:
⚡ All logic must complete within a single HTTP request
⚡ No persistent connections
⚡ No polling loops
⚡ WP-Cron only for light tasks (email, cleanup)
⚡ No real-time features

DEPLOYMENT:
1. Backup WordPress (database + files)
2. Upload loungenie-portal/ to /wp-content/plugins/
3. Activate plugin in WordPress Admin
4. Go to Settings → Permalinks → Save Changes (flush rules)
5. Test: Visit /portal and log in

VERIFICATION:
Run: wp eval-file loungenie-portal/tests/ProductionVerification.php

DOCUMENTATION:
- SETUP_GUIDE.md — Installation instructions
